{"tid":2151111,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"香港政研會主席以個人名義，於今天向證監會去信，正式投訴其未有即時停牌壹傳媒","createTime":"2020-08-11T08:38:15.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-11T15:41:00.000Z","uid":28114,"like":3,"dislike":14,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"b93ed60fea24a3c78022125887982955deea4b37","tid":2151111,"uid":28114,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-11T08:38:15.000Z","msg":"《異動股》壹傳媒（００２８２）爆升逾五倍，成交近２８億元<br />\n　　《經濟通通訊社１１日專訊》壹傳媒（００２８２）現價升５３１﹒３７％，報１﹒６１元；成交約２８﹒９３億股，涉資２７﹒６６億元。主房買盤達六成，盤中高見１﹒９６元破上市新高。　　據知香港政研會主席以個人名義，於今天向證監會去信，正式投訴其未有即時停牌壹傳媒，其指由於有關股票在市場大幅異動，或會損害投資者權益及影響港股交易市場聲譽，因此要求證監會儘快糾正錯誤馬上停牌壹傳媒，直至事件得到合理解釋為止。　　現時，恆生指數報２４９７７，升５９９點或升２﹒４６％，主板成交８３１﹒９６億元。國企指數報１０２２８，升２３７點或升２﹒３８％。　　即月期指新報２４９５７，升５５１點，低水２０點。即月國指期貨報１０２１５，升２１０點，低水１３點。　　上證綜合指數報３３９９，升２０點或升０﹒６１％，成交３３３２﹒１２億元人民幣。深證成份指數報１３７３８，升８０點或升０﹒５９％，成交４０３６﹒５１億元人民幣。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.etnet.com.hk/mobile/tc/news/categorized_news_detail.php?category=editorchoice&amp;newsid=ETN300811336\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.etnet.com.hk%2Fmobile%2Ftc%2Fnews%2Fcategorized_news_detail.php%3Fcategory%3Deditorchoice%26newsid%3DETN300811336&d=9ox5Qr7lvCKhSYdyRcf9FkPYNnpCCLo8Mp68exG%2FaA0%3D&h=e906bb99\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.etnet.com.hk/mobile/tc/news/categorized_news_detail.php?category=editorchoice&amp;newsid=ETN300811336</a>"},{"pid":"15087fa12cb4767727944140d55f03358e05d3a6","tid":2151111,"uid":38904,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-11T08:40:18.000Z","msg":"咁多傳媒訪問使撚你去開case file咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/silly.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8baa92b2e95a8dab816871c8c90c105c977f7c70","tid":2151111,"uid":263944,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-11T08:40:48.000Z","msg":"市場自由都冇埋<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dd3505646d35ef122570078a984134e3f269c9f6","tid":2151111,"uid":28114,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-11T08:42:01.000Z","msg":"股票都唔俾買<img