/2150727</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-08-11T08:46:33.000Z","msg":"香港政府就係聽佢地講研究政策? <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-11T08:58:19.000Z","msg":"佢地根本唔係做政策研究<br />\n佢個政研會同愛護香港力量都係土共整出黎去搞事<br />\n之前仲去港台門口示威 要政府將港台個頻譜交比政研會用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-11T09:17:23.000Z","msg":"Send his name and the shitty organization info for Sanction!"},{"pid":"e5645bc39ed8791a7ec8f181ab72a4fe7e24b561","tid":2151111,"uid":193100,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-11T14:03:18.000Z","msg":"證監會：將密切監察與壹傳媒股份有關交易活動<br />\n<br />\n證監會表示，因應壹傳媒近日股價及成交量大幅上升，證監會一直監察，並將繼續密切監察與壹傳媒股份有關的交易活動，亦將與聯交所合作，要求公司向市場及時披露所有與公司控制權、財務狀況及營運有關，並且可能對公司股價造成重大影響的未來發展情況及資料，避免證券出現虛假市場。證監會發表聲明，回應收到與壹傳媒股價及成交量大幅上升相關的大量查詢及公眾對事件的關注，表示由於壹傳媒股價及成交量的異常升幅，投資者買賣時務須格外審慎。<br />\n<br />\n2020-08-11 21:48:41<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1543173-20200811.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1543173-20200811.htm&d=9ox5Qr7lvCKhSYdyRcf9FkPYNnpCCLo8Mp68exG%2FaA0%3D&h=9cb4d5bc\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1543173-20200811.htm&h=0ccd6a51\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1543173-20200811.htm</a>"},{"pid":"9ded9ae177166684f9add526c8ff829360ff2595","tid":2151111,"uid":37525,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c46fd5d1a85deb96959086dfd0909e6829ff76a6","tid":2151111,"uid":97080,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"df250974f71eb91847582677673555b7f2108ffc","tid":2151111,"uid":68026,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"e4f391f54981a941654a78941d3443045d03f86e","tid":2151111,"uid":97080,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-11T08:43:39.000Z","msg":"即係邊個?"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-11T08:45:00.000Z","m